            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "got to a prestige and a half before a hard drive transfer and i lost all my levels........ but still one of my favorite games to this day!\n\none of the best arcade shooters of all time. one of the best storylines of all time! one of the best games that get a zombie mode to it. it shall never end!\n\nSolo story is amazing! 10/10, Multiplayer is nothing but a 10/10, Zombies........ Of course is 10/10! \n\nIts what we knew as kids, just with a slim player count. 10/10"
        },
        {
            "review_id": "225316043",
            "steam_id": "76561198147063745",
            "playtime_minutes": 353,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "It's just a good game. There are many others who would do a better job of describing how good this game is so I'll just say this. It's not worth 40 bucks in this day and age. This game is 16 years old and while that's not a bad thing it definitely shows. Hence why it's not worth that price. Wait until it's on discount."
