        {
            "review_id": "225163212",
            "steam_id": "76561198044828474",
            "playtime_minutes": 346,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 2,
            "weighted_score": 0.5454545617103577,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "I remember now why I have such a fond memory of this game. The numbers were a huge meme when this came out and everybody was talking about it. The whole setting just immediately pulls you in and you want to know what the numbers mean too. \n\nThe campaign was such a banger and I remember how I felt when I could first fly the helicopter back when the game came out. Also playing Fortunate Son while flying in with a bunch of hueys? Absolutely based. This is one of those Call of Duty games that makes you remember why it was so peak back then compared to now. \n\nHighly recommend for anyone who just wants to go through the franchise campaigns and especially for those who want to reexperience the nostalgia. Well worth it."
        },
        {
            "review_id": "226428239",
